Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.35,0:00:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm neither an angel or a devil
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.60,0:00:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Our hearts are just some broken refletion in someone else's mirror
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.68,0:00:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Choosing between options A and B
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.06,0:00:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,is according to the attitude of you who always walk on my right side
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.68,0:00:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I like the darkening blue of the skies after school
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.93,0:00:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't feel anything in a frenetic classoom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.35,0:00:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,In an angle that teachers can't see, somewhere parents don't know about,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.52,0:00:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,my heart is well hidden
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.77,0:00:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Good kids all start going home
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.85,0:01:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Black crows start cawing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.27,0:01:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,My reflection in you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.43,0:01:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,is a pure resonance trusts in people's hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.68,0:01:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason I don't say goodbye is because
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.81,0:01:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be penetrated by you
