Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.56,0:01:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The kids who only pretend to be earnest in front of teachers fill me with disgust
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.89,0:01:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,As I said so, you hanged your head in sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.14,0:01:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually I don't really care about this, the main subject is something else
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.47,0:01:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The badness is well hidden
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.56,0:01:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Good kids all grow into adults,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.81,0:01:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,wake up from their dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.22,0:01:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The memories of walking alongside you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.43,0:01:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and your back with sagacity started to fade
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.68,0:02:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason I don't say thank you is because
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.10,0:02:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to have any chance to be disliked by you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.81,0:02:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I am aware of all of my flaws
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.81,0:02:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The shadow strikes first
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.68,0:02:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time on our way home,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.81,0:02:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I become fragile as I drift away from you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.93,0:02:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H78&}The reason I don't say goodbye is because
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.18,0:02:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason I don't say goodbye is because
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to be swallowed by the loneliness
